Murtogg and Mullroy consider that point --

EXT. FORT CHARLES - DAY

Elizabeth, pale and perspiring, fans herself weakly,
oblivious to the music and chatter.

                    NORRINGTON
          May I have a moment?

He extends his arm. She takes it. He walks her away from
