Jack climbs up, exhausted. Elizabeth is on her back;
Murtogg holds her arms above her head, pumping them.
Mullroy puts his cheek to her nose and mouth.

                    MULLROY
          Not breathing.

Murtogg looks down; it seems hopeless. Jack steps up,
