Jack flips the knife and hands it hilt-first to Murtogg -
and that's when he spots -

The MEDALLION. Jack catches it up in his "hand.

                    JACK (CONT'D)
          Where did you get this?

Before Elizabeth can answer, the BLADE of a SWORD is at
