                    JACK (CONT'D)
          Elizabeth -- it is Elizabeth?

Elizabeth is more angry than frightened.

ELIZABETH Miss Swann.

                    JACK
          Miss Swann, if you'll be so kind?

She takes the belt and pistol from Norrington -- Jack's
