                    PINTEL
          I guess there is a reason to fret.

EXT. ISLA DE MUERTE - NIGHT

The Dauntless drifts into the lagoon. Norrington and his
men prepare to go ashore.     h

INT. ISLA DE MUERTA - CAVES - NIGHT

